    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good overall condition and has been well-maintained throughout its ownership. The engine runs smoothly and the transmission shifts precisely, making it a reliable choice for any driver. While the exterior retains a great shine, there are some minor surface scratches and small stone chips consistent with regular use. Inside, the cabin is clean and comfortable, though you may notice slight wear on the driver's seat bolster. All electronics and features are fully functional, and it has a solid service history, ensuring it is ready for the road without immediate needs.",
